name: Matt Lieb
bio: Matt Lieb is a comic and comedy writer from San Francisco, where he was named one of the "Best Comedians in the Bay Area" by SFist and Courting Comedy. Matt is a correspondent on The Star Wars Show on StarWars.com, a writer/performer on Al Jazeera's only comedy show Newsbroke, and staff writer for Audible's original series "Bedtime Stories for Cynics with Nick Offerman." Matt's stand up was featured on the show "Flophouse" on VICELAND, "The Guest List" on SeeSo, Gabriel Iglesias' "Stand Up Revolution Radio" on SiriusXM, and is featured on Hulu.
